<Layout>
  <PolicyPage
    badgeLabel="Terms of service"
    title="Our terms of service"
    headerDesc="Read our terms below to learn more about your rights and responsibilities as a YourCVVideo user."
    autherNameColor="text-slate-600"
    autherDateColor="text-slate-600"
    autherName="Published"
    autherDate={date}
  >
    <div class="text-slate-800 mb-8">
      <div class="mt-4">
        <h4 class="h4 font-playfair-display mb-2 mt-4 underline">
          DEFINITIONS
        </h4>

        <p>The 'Company' means YourCVVideo.com Ltd.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          The 'Client' means the person or business purchasing a subscription.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          The 'Plan' means the monthly Diamond Package pricing plan.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          The 'Product' means the Administration Portal, Recruiter Dashboard,
          the Website, and any other services or components that make up the
          YourCVVideo.com offering.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          End User' means the Candidate, Recruiter or any other visitor that
          uses the YourCVVideo.com website.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Qualified Application' means a Candidates application via the Website,
          where the application is, at YourCVVideo.com sole discretion, deemed
          to be genuine, and unique.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Qualified Candidate' means a candidate who on their application via
          the Website opted to share their details with the Recruiter, where the
          Candidate is, at YourCVVideo.com sole discretion, deemed to be
          genuine, and unique.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4">
